        "name": "雷达数据处理",
        "func": "// 存储雷达数据\ncontext.global.radarData = context.global.radarData || new Array(181).fill(0);\n\nvar angle = msg.payload.angle;\nvar distance = msg.payload.distance;\n\n// 更新对应角度的数据\ncontext.global.radarData[angle] = distance;\n\n// 返回处理后的数据\nmsg.payload = {\n    angle: angle,\n    distance: distance,\n    warning: msg.payload.warning,\n    radarData: context.global.radarData\n};\n\nreturn msg;",
